{
  "stem": "5388.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's where she lives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somebody takes her to there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, this whole story fell apart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[CLAPS] And they throw her into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when she was thrown into the ghetto, suddenly my father got wind, and [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Lisa ?] got wind, and Aaron, that I was arrested, that I'm in the ghetto [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Vaha. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were trying, kind of, to get-- it didn't get to anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they approached one gendarme there, and he kind of-- when I was in the washroom-- said, don't tell them that you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're doing fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, what are you-- I didn't know that he-- I said, I don't know what you're talking about.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so some of them-- that's it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, we just--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two minutes?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me wind up this particular story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this guy asked me to take off my shoe, because people who were running away were wearing a few shirts, two pair, three pair, four shirts.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only had one shirt, but I did have two pair of socks, and two pair of underwear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's cold in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that kind of pairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a little other problem on my hand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father gave me five-ruble gold piece before leaving, just in case of travel, I will need it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when he was pushing, all of the sudden, I didn't remember where I put the five ruble.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I moved it away from my pocket, and I put it into my boots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had boots on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember, that the policeman was on my right side, so I must have done it on the left side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I took off the right shoe.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
